+++Antagony+++

Antagony looked calmly at FZ and then stepped forward. She quickly glanced 
around the room and memorized it in her mind. Antagony always liked to know 
what was around her.

"Hello, Zardus," she said calmly, "my name is Antagony. I just woke up in my 
pod and Perndabot recruited me, but I want to join you. Is that ok?"
